20:05.240 --> 20:05.890
Betul!

20:05.910 --> 20:07.180
- Betul!
- Ya!

20:07.790 --> 20:08.480
Kenapa kamu menipu?

20:08.480 --> 20:09.280
Ketua aliran,

20:09.310 --> 20:10.480
